  <brief_title>Hypercoagulable Parameters as Predictors of Thrombotic Events and Prognosis in Patients With Advanced Non-Small Cell Lung Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hypercoagulable Parameters as Predictors of Thrombotic Events and Prognosis in Patients With Advanced Non-Small Cell Lung Carcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
